lead_paragraph: Tottenham Hotspur became the latest club to join the soccer drive in China as the Premier League side will take part in a year-long initiative to develop the game at grassroots level in the Asian country.

headline.print_headline: Tottenham Join Drive to Promote Youth Football in China
